title: Kaela Kimura - ROCK
description:
"ROCK" is Kimura's first release from her private label 'ELA' that she established under Victor Entertainment. She covered songs from artists of the 1960s, '70s, and '80s that have influenced her. A total of 12 artists such as Saito Kazuyoshi, Chara, Chatmonchy, and Shigeru Kishida have joined her to cover the songs.
